<para>-Border-color related CSS properties: <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border">border</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-top-color">border-top-color</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-right-color">border-right-color</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-bottom-color">border-bottom-color</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-left-color">border-left-color</see>,<br/>-Other border-related CSS properties: <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-width">border-width</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-style">border-style</see><br/>-The {{CSSxRef(&amp;quot;&amp;lt;color&amp;gt;&amp;quot;)}} data type<br/>-Other color-related properties: <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color">color</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/background-color">background-color</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/outline-color">outline-color</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/text-decoration-color">text-decoration-color</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/text-emphasis-color">text-emphasis-color</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/text-shadow">text-shadow</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/caret-color">caret-color</see>, and <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-rule-color">column-rule-color</see><br/>-<see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_colors/Applying_color">Applying color to HTML elements using CSS</see><br/></para>
